description:
*From Homeless to Outreach* | If God pulled you out of homeless, would you pay it forward and help others? Hear the powerful testimony of a young man, Eric, who was homeless for years and how he used that experience to help other homeless individuals get access to showers, clean clothes, food, and even a job and home. @saltoutreachstories1133
